{"tid":98102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京人狂燒炮仗 PM2.5最高飆至724","createTime":"2017-01-28T07:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T20:04:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9094d7173ab3a70af8e31e83f4c32ffd913a3042","tid":98102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"毒霧已經成為北京人的日常，但過年還是要燒炮仗！昨晚凌晨零時過後，大批民眾開始燃放炮仗，慶祝雞年的來臨。當地空氣質素極速惡化，PM 2.5濃度急升，官方公佈的數字聲稱最高字達647，但將數據換算至美國標準，數字則升至724，達到嚴重污染的水平。 <br />\n<br />\n北京的環保部門指出，從昨晚9時起民眾狂放炮仗，全市空氣開始極速污染，PM2.5濃度進一步躍升，凌晨2時達到峰值濃度647微克/立方米，為近五年同期的第二高值。 <br />\n<br />\n然而，將數據換算至美國的環保標準，數字則升至724，至今早11時，PM 2.5濃度亦達317，達危害水平。 <br />\n<br />\n中新網"},{"pid":"5e3c524dca7b9ef2319d1d725354ced5ab43ffee","tid":98102,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"終於搵到野賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9716a19f3c08462fbbf9bee8937df285b93e6520","tid":98102,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2bd16e3f6b3aec331b3cd49f502f0653f25f82","tid":98102,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:17:03.000Z","msg":"米諾夫斯基粒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5bd4a2ea551181b92709d90890e410eb00c4f5d","tid":98102,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be4abfd9eb2f067425d2b55a91634feddfad074","tid":98102,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:2